:17:32.000Z","raceComments":"{\"comment\":\"1. SWIFT DRAGON was a dominant QTIS Jewel winner in his penultimate start, and then ran a huge race in the Pat O’Shea Plate at Toowoomba when well supported. He can make full use of the pole position here, and he can remain unbeaten on this track. 2. BETTER BLITZEM was not far off the top pick in the Jewel, and his record of 4 wins from 5 starts says he is a colt with a bright future. He has the early speed to offset his wide gate, and he is capable of turning the tables. 5. COAL SEAM was beaten by a short head here fresh in an Open 2YO, and he looks like a gelding with genuine upside. He maps to receive the run of the race, and he loses nothing with Justin P Stanley in the irons. 9. MISSILE BABY showed real grit on debut to score here on debut when holding off the third pick, and he will give his trainer, Clint Taylor, a strong hand in this rich race. He cops a wide gate, but can't be taken lightly. Stick with him.\",\"runners\":[1,2,5,9],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Russell Leonard","tipRunnerNumbers":[1,9,2,5]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,5,9]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,5,7]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,7,5]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,9,5]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,5,8,9]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,3,5]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,1,5,9]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"ROC","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"RO